# ── Production deployment artefacts (NEVER commit — see CHANGELOG) ──────────
# These catch live operator inventories / env files at any depth. Templates
# live alongside as `*.example` (e.g. `deploy/inventory/production.ini.example`)
# and stay versioned.
# (The older `deploy/inventory/production.ini` literal line below is kept as a
# re-anchor so the path is still matched even without `**/`. The `**/`
# patterns above are the canonical coverage.)
deploy/inventory/production.ini
**/production.ini
**/inventory.ini
**/inventory.yml
**/inventory.yaml
**/production.env
**/.env.production

# ── Ansible inventory (real IPs/hosts — NEVER commit the live file) ──
# Legacy anchor kept for clarity (now double-covered by the rules above).

